#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:4
msgid "Version Guarantees"
msgstr "版本保證"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:6
msgid ""
"The library follows a `semantic versioning principle <https://semver.org/>`_ "
"which means that the major version is updated every time there is an "
"incompatible API change. However due to the lack of guarantees on the "
"Discord side when it comes to breaking changes along with the fairly dynamic "
"nature of Python it can be hard to discern what can be considered a breaking "
"change and what isn't."
msgstr ""
"此程式庫遵循 `語意化版本原則 <https://semver.org/>`_，這表示每當有不相容的 "
"API 變更時，主要版本號就會更新。然而，由於 Discord 方面對破壞性變更缺乏保證，"
"加上 Python 本身的動態特性，有時很難區分什麼算是破壞性變更，什麼不算。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:8
msgid ""
"The first thing to keep in mind is that breaking changes only apply to "
"**publicly documented functions and classes**. If it's not listed in the "
"documentation here then it is not part of the public API and is thus bound "
"to change. This includes attributes that start with an underscore or "
"functions without an underscore that are not documented."
msgstr ""
"首先要記住的是，破壞性變更僅適用於**公開文件中的函數與類別**。如果某個項目未"
"列在此處的文件中，則它不屬於公開 API 的一部分，因此可能會變更。這包括以底線開"
"頭的屬性，或是沒有底線但未記載於文件中的函數。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:12
msgid "The examples below are non-exhaustive."
msgstr "以下範例並非詳盡列舉。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:15
msgid "Examples of Breaking Changes"
msgstr "破壞性變更的範例"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:17
msgid "Changing the default parameter value to something else."
msgstr "將預設參數值更改為其他值。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:18
msgid "Renaming a function without an alias to an old function."
msgstr "重新命名函數但未提供指向舊函數的別名。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:19
msgid "Adding or removing parameters to an event."
msgstr "對事件新增或移除參數。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:22
msgid "Examples of Non-Breaking Changes"
msgstr "非破壞性變更的範例"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:24
msgid "Adding or removing private underscored attributes."
msgstr "新增或移除私有底線屬性。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:25
msgid "Adding an element into the ``__slots__`` of a data class."
msgstr "在資料類別的 ``__slots__`` 中新增元素。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:26
msgid "Changing the behaviour of a function to fix a bug."
msgstr "修改函數行為以修正錯誤。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:27
msgid "Changes in the typing behaviour of the library."
msgstr "程式庫的型別標註行為變更。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:28
msgid ""
"Changes in the calling convention of functions that are primarily meant as "
"callbacks."
msgstr "主要用作回呼（callback）的函數之呼叫慣例變更。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:29
msgid "Changes in the documentation."
msgstr "文件內容的變更。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:30
msgid "Modifying the internal HTTP handling."
msgstr "修改內部的 HTTP 處理方式。"

#: ../../../version_guarantees.rst:31
msgid "Upgrading the dependencies to a new version, major or otherwise."
msgstr "將依賴項目升級至新版本，無論是主要版本或其他版本。"
